msgstr "Утишавање слоја"

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/layers.page:59
msgid ""
"To mute a layer, click <gui>Volume icon</gui>. The icon will be toggled to "
"show the layer has been muted. To unmute a layer, click <gui>Volume icon</"
